{"tid":321132,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得mnet idols school d女幾正？","createTime":"2017-07-14T05:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-15T11:45:21.000Z","uid":79981,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"89dba2cbd00463be25866555a4a83142df56396e","tid":321132,"uid":79981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:09:50.000Z","msg":"睇完第一集 佢地d樣係幾高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擺低少少資料先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n《偶像學校》（朝鮮語：아이돌 학교，英语：Idols School）為韓國Mnet2017年製作的綜藝節目，節目以養成新女團成員為主軸，招收學生後，於節目中進行訓練，預計訓練11週，優秀學生將能以新女團成員的身份出道。 節目於2017年7月13日開播。<br />\nformer sm trainee：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/125457_371a4925ac86c4b7c21bedaa39b43d01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F125457_371a4925ac86c4b7c21bedaa39b43d01.jpg&h=a4581848&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSeo Herin 2002/02/26<br />\nFormer JYP trainee:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/125747_f84e76a4c6fda69ab56cf3e8f7fa2d96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F125747_f84e76a4c6fda69ab56cf3e8f7fa2d96.jpg&h=2e0897b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNatty 2002/5/30<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/125816_c56b211ad06e2c676a9bcf434df4bd3a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F125816_c56b211ad06e2c676a9bcf434df4bd3a.jpg&h=d2dd9bd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPark Jiwon 1998/03/20<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/125846_8ac89fa56f2b03ea3118b3e623c7cd5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F125846_8ac89fa56f2b03ea3118b3e623c7cd5a.jpg&h=5d4ee9ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKim Eunsuh 2000/11/14<br />\n<br />\n好似仲有一個都係 不過果個無上sixteen confirm左再後補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nformer YG trainee:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/130102_2b2b66f805d6681db8ed1e9d2df38466.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F130102_2b2b66f805d6681db8ed1e9d2df38466.jpg&h=66d0f578&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLee seoyeon 1999/01/22<br />\n<br />\nProduce 101:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/130211_448855b882e70dd94b661e5c3a258ff2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F130211_448855b882e70dd94b661e5c3a258ff2.jpg&h=41fc1e7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLee Haein 1994/07/04<br />\n<br />\n暫時覺得呢個幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/130416_51afd3604ae0915c6f57337f13a2f7fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F130416_51afd3604ae0915c6f57337f13a2f7fa.jpg&h=75fc9b6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBaek Jiheon 2003/04/17<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多人 遲下慢慢up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你地覺得邊個正入嚟幫佢擦下存在感啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見到sixteen果幾個都有進步幾開心 加油阿佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc6a19798ab3ddb14b843370137120903f639b3","tid":321132,"uid":53488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T12:02:30.000Z","msg":"herin!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一定要成功出道"},{"pid":"e34cb2fdc95036bd07c052de05e283f15422be44","tid":321132,"uid":89411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T12:19:07.000Z","msg":"有無中字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 